1. *Pričajte* mi o vašem putovanju. (Tell me about your trip.) 
2. Možete li *pričati* tiše, molim vas? (Can you speak more quietly, please?) 
3. Sviđa mi se kad mi prijatelji *pričaju* viceve. (I like it when my friends tell me jokes.) 
4. Ne mogu sad *pričati* telefonom, zovite me kasnije. (I can't talk on the phone now, call me later.) 
5. Kako da *pričam* s njim ako ne znam njegov broj telefona? (How can I talk to him if I don't know his phone number?) 
6. Oni će *pričati* o tome na sastanku sutra. (They will discuss it at the meeting tomorrow.) 
7. Molim vas, *pričajte* polako, nisam dobro razumela. (Please speak slowly, I didn't understand well.) 
8. Kad *pričam* o tome, osjećam se bolje. (When I talk about it, I feel better.) 
9. Mogli bismo *pričati* o ovome cijelu noć. (We could talk about this all night.) 
10. *Pričajmo* o tome kasnije, sada se moramo posvetiti ovom zadatku. (Let's talk about it later, now we need to focus on this task.)